headline: E-Z-GO® Introduces All-New Liberty™ Vehicle for 2027 Model Year
summary: Textron E-Z-GO LLC, a Textron Inc. (NYSE: TXT) company, announces the next generation of its groundbreaking E-Z-GO® Liberty™ vehicle for the 2027 model year, redesigned from the ground up to offer an unparalleled ride, whether it's traveling the neighborhood or traversing the golf course.
